      "html": "<p>“agent noun” 源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of dry \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/dry\">dry</a>（动词），请参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of drier \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/drier\">drier</a>。</p>"
    }
  ]
